Silvercorp Says Consumers Need Protection From Short Sellers

-- B y   S o n j a   E l m q u i s t
-- 
2011-09-20T15:35:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/silvercorp-says-consumers-need-protection-from-short-sellers.html
North American securities
regulators need to protect consumers from short sellers who
spread rumors to depress a stock price,  Silvercorp Metals Inc. (SVM) 
Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Rui Feng said.  Feng made the comments today in a speech to miners and
investors at the Denver Gold Forum in  Colorado  Springs,
Colorado.  To contact the reporter on this story:
